      <p>Avarage rating: <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star" aria-hidden="true"></span><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star" aria-hidden="true"></span><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star" aria-hidden="true"></span><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star" aria-hidden="true"></span><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty" aria-hidden="true"></span> </p>
